    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it's been super reliable for me. It's in really great shape and has been well-cared for over the years\u2014it still drives like a dream and looks fantastic on the road! You might find a tiny bit of character from normal use, but it's honestly a wonderful, solid ride that's ready for its next adventure. I'm looking for a good home for it, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
